'''Acción Ecológica''' is one of the main environmental organizations based in [[Ecuador]]. It is based in [[Quito]].

They campaign on a range of issues including oil extraction, exploration and pipeline transport, [[Amazon Rainforest]] protection, [[food sovereignty]], [[biofuels]] and plantations for [[carbon offset]]s.

