The '''Institute of Petroleum Engineering (IPE)''' is a specialised centre in teaching, training and research with the largest [[Petroleum engineering|Petroleum Engineering]] research programme in the UK. Founded in 1975 and based in the city of [[Edinburgh]], IPE has expanded to the far reaches of Scotland in the Orkney Islands, and internationally, into the Middle East & Asia through its Approved Learning Partnerships.

