The '''Roşieşti Wind Farm''' is a proposed [[wind power]] project in [[Vaslui County]], [[Romania]]. It will have 46 individual [[wind turbine]]s<ref>[http://www.standard.ro/articol_60388/e_on_investeste_in_prima_transa_pana_la_170_mil______in_trei_parcuri_eoliene.html E.ON investeste in prima transa de parcuri eoliene {{ro}}]</ref> with a nominal output of around 1 [[Watt#Megawatt|MW]] which will deliver up to 46 MW of power, enough to power over 18,216 homes, with a capital investment required of approximately US$104 million.

